{"tid":2274123,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Twitter 封鎖侵其中一篇新tweet留言同讚好功能","createTime":"2020-11-06T08:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T09:01:26.000Z","uid":80567,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"54c5657660e81209b129a514b77ddc3f33672a26","tid":2274123,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:32:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1324613181466173440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1324613181466173440&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9ptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=591aba8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1324613181466173440&h=ffd2c961\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1324613181466173440</a><br />\n<br />\n隨後侵再開twitter片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1324613375213621248\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1324613375213621248&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9ptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=8e76d1c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1324613375213621248&h=49a564c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1324613375213621248</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>題外話：</strong><br />\n<br />\nSection 230係咩呢？<br />\n第一修正案係保障言論自由，包括hate speech<br />\n至於Section 230就同First Amendment有關<br />\n<blockquote>第230條通常被視為社交平臺的保護傘，因為它容許社交平臺不必承擔使用者所張貼內容的責任，同時也賦予它們出自於善意、限制平臺上所出現之冒犯性內容的權力。臉書、Google或Twitter在面臨相關訴訟時，也廣泛地引用該條款來保障自己，並經常因此而勝訴。</blockquote><br />\n換句話講即係social media可以免於為用戶嘅言論負責<br />\n推而廣之就係將該平台所認定嘅fake news flag起佢，而唔牴觸First Amendment<br />\n所以成日被flag嘅侵就不滿，認為媒體過份解讀Section 230嘅內容<br />\n<br />\n另一方意見係：<br />\n上星期喺senate舉行嘅聽證會<br />\nTwitter、Facebook、Google CEO都不約而同認為唔應該刪去Section 230<br />\n或者要好小心地修改<br />\n佢哋話當social media冇咗Section 230嘅保障，只會有更多censorship"},{"pid":"cef21de4ac5d886ce0a70ecab9aa7a67f9c8b5d3","tid":2274123,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99dc1b1a18244b198244fe21166f4882172ab3b6","tid":2274123,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:42:30.000Z","msg":"咁企業唔想出事， 實搵人mon post,  del post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22d09a612565e050fe6e8114dadb7e684c78b2a","tid":2274123,"uid":296369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:55:41.000Z","msg":"Twitter 遲啲都會要受罰！"},{"pid":"3d0961158214e686dfed22174059ecdeeafff16b","tid":2274123,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd11dceb36bc6ce799e7c62f0ac3d3e1ef4c44f6","tid":2274123,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:01:26.000Z","msg":"Evil Twitter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}